{"tid":1177134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】點解公眾人物唔可以唔表態","createTime":"2019-05-29T15:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T15:09:23.000Z","uid":92459,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c4dac96357e8e5cc1b8e93a2dc319e4aca5a82d6","tid":1177134,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"因為沉默是幫兇<br />\n香港生死存亡之際仲可以唔表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為公眾人物，危急關頭唔發揮影響力<br />\n香港你地冇份? <br />\n香港有事都唔幫手，咁就唔好叫自己做香港人，唔好靠香港人賺錢<br />\n吾雖不殺伯仁，伯仁由我而死。<br />\n明明影響力大過好多人，但係就咩都唔做，咁同幫兇有咩分別，你地對得住香港?"},{"pid":"51556c9e5b5dd78f80b9cfefe1b7c84c916b596d","tid":1177134,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71ff8a40724dec3642fa27d10e1d16bcdb3ce3f","tid":1177134,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"拎曬外國護照隨時走人嗰班我都明佢諗乜。但嗰走唔到，共產黨打到黎嗰時一樣要硬食嗰班友，呢家都唔出句聲做啲野真係痴撚線。真係以為政治唔關自己事，可以獨善其身？"},{"pid":"da7d50ee123f1f9b8213d86c3a17b7ceeb31bc2f","tid":1177134,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3686df2abc430c6131373580e40adc8f16bd8f3","tid":1177134,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2d95cca54c0feb745eb6e9f2cf084459af8f39","tid":1177134,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正